collections.name: Hexabite - Project : Unknown_Seoul
collections.description:
The Invisible Line of Defense: HEXABITE

HEXABITE is an independent tactical security unit under UNI-OM, responsible for critical security operations throughout the city.
From infrastructure protection and public order enforcement to VIP security and high-risk target elimination,
it operates as a unified force capable of responding to a wide range of threats with strategic precision.

We operate in the blind spots where conventional forces hesitate,
prioritizing the safety of the city and the interests of the corporation.

Before uncontrolled chaos can spread, we are the first to move - the line that holds before order collapses.

Even now, we remain in the unseen, preserving the balance of the city.
